Uses of Package
net.proteusframework.ui.miwt

  • Packages that use net.proteusframework.ui.miwt 
    Package Description
    net.proteusframework.ui.column
    Column based table / tree API.
    net.proteusframework.ui.miwt
    MIWT is a web toolkit for rapidly building user interfaces.
    net.proteusframework.ui.miwt.component
    This package is for primitive components.
    net.proteusframework.ui.miwt.component.composite
    This package is for composite components which are components that are built from other components.
    net.proteusframework.ui.miwt.component.composite.editor
    Classes to help implement property editor patterns.
    net.proteusframework.ui.miwt.component.event
    Events specific to components live here.
    net.proteusframework.ui.miwt.event
    Events not specific to another package and classes that manage events live here.
    net.proteusframework.ui.miwt.input
    Defines a generic input system that a medium implementation may use.
    net.proteusframework.ui.miwt.layout
    Use of layout API is deprecated.
    net.proteusframework.ui.miwt.locale
    Provides an internationalization framework for MIWT.
    net.proteusframework.ui.miwt.resource
    MIWT resources.
    net.proteusframework.ui.miwt.util
    Classes in this package provide some helper methods.
    net.proteusframework.ui.search
    Classes for modeling search criteria, results, and UI needs.
    net.proteusframework.ui.workspace
    The workspace API provides a framework for managing UIs based on tasks and events.
  • Classes in net.proteusframework.ui.miwt used by net.proteusframework.ui.column 
    Class and Description
    Pageable
    This interface should be implemented by components that support paging, ie the ability to view a component a page at a time.
  • Classes in net.proteusframework.ui.miwt used by net.proteusframework.ui.miwt 
    Class and Description
    AbstractAction
    This class provides default implementations for the Action interface.
    Action
    The Action interface provides a useful extension to the ActionListener interface in cases where the same functionality may be accessed by several controls.
    ActionDefinition
    Action definition.
    ActionFactory
    Factory for creating action based objects.
    ButtonGroup
    This class is used to create a multiple-exclusion scope for a set of buttons.
    CannotCloseMIWTException
    Exception thrown when trying to close a Component when it cannot be closed.
    Color
    Represents a color.
    Device
    The device class abstracts device characters that the WindowManager is using for display.
    Direction
    Type safe enumeration of directions using compass directions as names.
    History
    Implements a History list.
    HistoryElement
    HistoryElement instances are used to populate a History object to hold the history of Components.
    HorizontalJustification
    Type-safe enumeration describing horizontal justification.
    Image
    Represents an image.
    ImageFill
    Type safe enumeration for image fill methods.
    MIWTApplication
    Class that all MIWT applications must extend.
    MIWTException
    Base exception for MIWT exceptions.
    MIWTSession
    An MIWTSession object holds the necessary objects to support running a set of applications for a single user's session.
    Orientation
    Type-safe enumeration for orientation, horizontal or vertical.
    ReflectiveAction
    Action implementation that takes an Object and method name to call when the Action is fired.
    Timer
    A Timer object calls tasks to be executed at a specified time and/or interval.
    WindowManager
    The WindowManager manages the presentation, medium and event dispatch layers for one session of any number of MIWT applications.
    WindowScrollCallback
    Window scrolling callback.
    WindowScrollPosition
    Scroll position.
    WindowUpdateContext
    Context information for a Window update operation.
    WindowUpdateInitiator
    Initiator of a window update.
